   :topic: Chapter3/ConvertingFromDoubleToInt
   :from_source: T
   :language: cpp
   :caption: Double to Int

   Convert the price to an int. Then use a print statement to observe the output!
   ~~~~
   #include <iostream>
   using namespace std;

   int main () {
       double price = 6.98;
       int sale_price;
       cout << sale_price;
       return 0;
   }